{"tid":1044672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"否認有線新聞部裁員 邱達昌：已在大灣區開設新聞中心","createTime":"2019-03-03T05:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T22:25:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3b37f892822e13335b6683fb88214e3e58056bd2","tid":1044672,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:33:18.000Z","msg":"今年1月有報道指有線新聞部會裁員近50人，身在北京出席全國政協會議的有線寬頻主席、全國政協委員邱達昌今天開腔回應：「都無咁嘅事！」他稱新聞部日後會否進行架構重整，要由新任有線新聞執行董事馮德雄決定，強調自己不會「睇得咁細」。<br />\n有線寬頻上周宣佈，馮德雄將於本月13日出任有線新聞執行董事，有線新聞及有線體育執行董事趙應春則榮休，轉任有線寬頻主席特別顧問。邱達昌讚揚馮德雄是有經驗的資深新聞工作者，有信心他會做得好。<br />\n談及有線新聞部日後的發展方向，邱達昌指，有線已經在大灣區開設新聞中心，他個人認為大灣區非常「實在」，不單對香港發展有幫助，更為年輕人帶來商機。<br />\n有線寬頻早前傳出裁員消息，指資方將裁減新聞部約50人，佔該部門員工約一成；據悉向新聞部開刀的主意，來自與邱達昌關係友好的無綫行政總裁李寶安。另外，有線去年8月曾大裁員，娛樂新聞組幾乎全組解僱，形象宣傳部十多名資深員工被裁，體育組、工程部及行政部亦有逾20名員工被裁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190303/large/1551589002_bc3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190303%2Flarge%2F1551589002_bc3e.jpg&h=d811e456&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b96904a4685cb33b0cf2a841c4dff584f3b9b35c","tid":1044672,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T08:56:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9755f00d48d6c0ee01b753bdd07814721a3f75a","tid":1044672,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c467d93e9ce77efb9d552eac14a4cbdf8753cd85","tid":1044672,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"老邱啲後代，一係車死人，一係搞果樣死果樣。"},{"pid":"c719f6c2c2bb47b750fb6efd26b02bac5918d9d0","tid":1044672,"uid":193642,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"條友到底知唔知新聞部最重要嘅係咩?<br />\n大灣區開新聞中心真係on99"},{"pid":"cfd1052f2560d3ecce11d72ffba639ed5a19ca8f","tid":1044672,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友到底知唔知新聞部最重要嘅係咩?<br />\n大灣區開新聞中心真係on99</blockquote><br />\n最重咪就係奶共，然後收維穩費"},{"pid":"71e698367f2668662f5f729e0198175700e8ef61","tid":1044672,"uid":202698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:53:02.000Z","msg":"呢條傻仔，明知電視做唔住，死都要充大頭鬼"},{"pid":"25b319169c9f3b93677ba2a7cbc603a9d03bbc42","tid":1044672,"uid":188282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"cls大灣區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de59d8f62d233aae5d90819d5c6e3fae67214b3","tid":1044672,"uid":71635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"報緊大陸負面新聞<br />\n畫面轉頭影住個主播俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56dc08d4ff10b5a06485f7c4ff2c23a22ac4d98e","tid":1044672,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25b319169c9f3b93677ba2a7cbc603a9d03bbc42","tid":1044672,"uid":188282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"cls大灣區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5b7cc2faa26b112a793566476d8388d566d520","tid":1044672,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T21:23:42.000Z","msg":"now有得陽歐聯之後 諗唔到九咩理由睇有線"},{"pid":"9c4287af2a2d102130162f199007b1e606c6033b","tid":1044672,"uid":84585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T22:22:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b5fe8e1b9c7a15c4102a523aef0eb2e9fd56f83","tid":1044672,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T22:25:42.000Z","msg":"即係邊撚度"}]}